org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem

Class FilteringDirectoryNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.FilteringDirectoryNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Entry>, DirectoryEntry, Entry 

    public class FilteringDirectoryNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements DirectoryEntry
    A DirectoryEntry filter, which exposes another DirectoryEntry less certain parts. This is typically used when copying or comparing Filesystems.(Diretoryentry过滤器，它公开另一个Diretoryentry不太确定的部分。这通常用于复制或比较文件系统时。)

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      FilteringDirectoryNode(DirectoryEntry directory, java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> excludes)
      Creates a filter round the specified directory, which will exclude entries such as "MyNode" and "MyDir/IgnoreNode".(在指定的目录中创建一个过滤器，它将排除诸如“MyNode”和“MyDir/IgnoreNode”之类的条目。)

    • Constructor Detail

      • FilteringDirectoryNode

        public FilteringDirectoryNode(DirectoryEntry directory,
                              java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> excludes)
        Creates a filter round the specified directory, which will exclude entries such as "MyNode" and "MyDir/IgnoreNode". The excludes can stretch into children, if they contain a /.(在指定的目录中创建一个过滤器，它将排除诸如“MyNode”和“MyDir/IgnoreNode”之类的条目。如果包含/，则排除项可以扩展到子项。)
        Parameters:
        directory - The Directory to filter(目录-要过滤的目录)
        excludes - The Entries to exclude(排除-要排除的收件箱)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if directory is null(Java.lang. IllegalArgumentExcept-如果目录为空)

      • delete

        public boolean delete()
        Description copied from interface: Entry
        Delete this Entry. This operation should succeed, but there are special circumstances when it will not: If this Entry is the root of the Entry tree, it cannot be deleted, as there is no way to create another one. If this Entry is a directory, it cannot be deleted unless it is empty.(删除此条目。此操作应该成功，但在特殊情况下不会成功：如果此条目是条目树的根，则无法删除它，因为无法创建另一个条目。如果此条目是目录，则除非为空，否则无法删除。)
        Specified by:
        delete in interface Entry(在界面中删除条目)
        Returns:
        true if the Entry was successfully deleted, else false(如果该条目已成功删除，则为真，否则为假)

      • renameTo

        public boolean renameTo(java.lang.String newName)
        Description copied from interface: Entry
        Rename this Entry. This operation will fail if: There is a sibling Entry (i.e., an Entry whose parent is the same as this Entry's parent) with the same name. This Entry is the root of the Entry tree. Its name is dictated by the Filesystem and many not be changed.(删除此条目。如果存在兄弟条目（即，父代与此条目的父代相同的条目）具有相同名称。此条目是条目树的根。它的名称由文件库指定，许多名称不可更改。)
        Specified by:
        renameTo in interface Entry(界面条目中的重命名为)
        Parameters:
        newName - the new name for this Entry(newName -此条目的新名称)
        Returns:
        true if the operation succeeded, else false(如果操作成功，则为真，否则为假)
